---
title: Refinement routing — which agents re-run after a tweak
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Marketer
    participant P as Refinement panel
    participant R as ReAct router
    participant Pipe as Agent subset
    participant S as Output state

    U->>P: move a slider or type a request
    P->>R: POST /refine with the full output_state (stateless)
    Note over R: read slider changes and message, apply routing rules
    R-->>P: agents_to_run + routing_label + reasoning
    Note over R,Pipe: order is enforced, guardrails always follows copywriter
    P->>Pipe: re-run only the chosen agents
    Pipe-->>S: merge updated fields back into state
    S-->>U: patch only the affected report sections and show the routing label
